snippet.title: PixelJunk Shooter Ultimate - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
PixelJunk Shooter Ultimate is out Ultimate unites PixelJunk Shooter and Shooter 2 into one continuous experience, with host of enhancements. Driving the actions is a massive physics engine that features a powerful fluid dynamics system. While making your way through the game you'll quickly notice that the interplay between states of matter (solids, liquids, and gasses) is key to getting by. 

http://blog.us.playstation.com/tag/pixeljunk-shooter-ultimate/
